{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/whenDefined","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry\"><code>CustomElementRegistry</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/define\"><code>define()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/get\"><code>get()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/upgrade\"><code>upgrade()</code></a></li><li><em><code>whenDefined()</code></em></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  The <strong><code>whenDefined()</code></strong> method of the\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry\"><code>CustomElementRegistry</code></a> interface returns a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> that\n  resolves when the named element is defined.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js-nolint notranslate\">whenDefined(name)\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"name\"><code>name</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The name of the custom element.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> that fulfills with the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_custom_elements\">custom element</a>'s constructor when a custom element becomes defined with the given name. If a custom element has already been defined with the name, the promise will immediately fulfill.</p>\n<p>The promise is rejected with a <code>SyntaxError</code> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a> if the name is not a <a href=\"(https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/custom-elements.html#valid-custom-element-name)\">valid custom element name</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  This example uses <code>whenDefined()</code> to detect when the custom elements that\n  make up a menu are defined. The menu displays placeholder content until the actual menu\n  content is ready to display.\n</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>nav</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu-container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu-placeholder<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Loading…<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>nav-menu</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item 1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item 2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    …\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item N<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>nav-menu</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>nav</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> container <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'menu-container'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> placeholder <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> container<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.menu-placeholder'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Fetch all the children of menu that are not yet defined.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> undefinedElements <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> container<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelectorAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">':not(:defined)'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">removePlaceholder</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> promises <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>undefinedElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> customElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">whenDefined</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>button<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>localName<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Wait for all the children to be upgraded</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> Promise<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>promises<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// then remove the placeholder</span>\n  container<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>placeholder<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">removePlaceholder</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/custom-elements.html#dom-customelementregistry-whendefined-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/whenDefined/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The whenDefined() method of the\n  CustomElementRegistry interface returns a Promise that\n  resolves when the named element is defined.","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-09-13T13:39:19.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/customelementregistry/whendefined","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content